data.value:
Made with love for growing kiddos, every serving provides 50mg of DHA Omega-3 to help support brain and eye health, along with prebiotics and a good source of choline.
Certified USDA Organic
8g Protein per serving
25% DV Calcium per serving
Always organic, always delicious.
Our pasture-raised cows graze outside in the fresh air 120 days or more each year.
Our cows eat an all-organic, non-GMO diet and are not treated with antibiotics or added growth hormones.
Our farmers do not use prohibited pesticides* on their cropland or farms.
Storage Instruction: Keep Refrigerated. Do not microwave.
Reccomended: Horizon Organic Whole Milk is intended for individuals seeking a nutritious, organic dairy option rich in essential nutrients like protein, calcium, and vitamin D, suitable for ages 1 and older.
Ingredients:
Grade A Organic Milk, Chicory Root Extract†, DHA Algal Oil†, Ascorbic Acid and Tocopherols (Vitamin C and Vitamin E to Help Maintain Freshness)†, Choline Chloride†, Vitamin D3††.
Ingredient not found in regular milk. Ingredient in excess of amount permitted in regular milk.
